{"tid":216861,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[HKU] 龍華絕對唔係fm所想嘅烏托邦","createTime":"2017-04-25T13:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T04:59:16.000Z","uid":9561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1e5f13c654dee271bb420c7bd554267c59ea8b69","tid":216861,"uid":9561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T13:05:53.000Z","msg":"見連登好似冇開過龍華post<br />\n小弟就開番個同大家講下入面嘅黑暗野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實好多人都知龍華係一個「城外嘅人想入黎，城內嘅人想出去」嘅地方，而唔係好似喺某d fm眼中嘅「齋住嘅酒店」咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n正所謂天下烏鴉一樣黑，hall有hall嘅濕鳩，龍華一樣有佢嘅濕鳩之處<br />\n講真大家搞活動開開心心咪得，都係為左readmission架啦<br />\n但有好多自以為好有料嘅team leader 恃住自己識得少少technical野就隨意屌鳩d member，以為自己manage上市公司咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n亦有好多人搞埋晒d 冇料嘅hea活動博readmission，搞到 readmission point水漲船高，好多人都拿捏唔到玩幾多先住到落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n歡迎龍華人發洩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：小弟住過一年，頂唔順quit左"},{"pid":"2c7b9536b86a808ad2a9887100e1319ffc40681f","tid":216861,"uid":34170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"要點先入到龍華？<br />\n靠interview?"},{"pid":"631e8e8ac555ffbcff3fc28df27f7d55b18a0494","tid":216861,"uid":9561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T14:17:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要點先入到龍華？<br />\n靠interview?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多數係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過有d block好似唔洗"},{"pid":"d3f8edf250a2e94e1d6bb87e9d5ae22dfd719743","tid":216861,"uid":80397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T05:33:22.000Z","msg":"住過兩年<br />\n做過某某exco  但同tutor唔熟<br />\nFinal year readmit 唔到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好同意龍華一樣有圈子 <br />\n毒撚難做 <img src=\"/assets/face